Installation:

	git clone git://github.com/rgaertne/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

	ln -s ~/dotfiles/vimrc ~/.vimrc

Add plugins to repo:

	cd ~/.vim/bundle
	git submodule add <url to plugin git repo> bundle/<plugin>
	git add .
	git commit -m "commit comment"


Obtain plugins:
	
	git submodule init
	git submodule update
	
Update plugins:

	cd ~/.vim/bundle/<plugin>
	git pull

